data.name: ElementChange
desc: This structure describes a single change that is part of a batch of changes.

items.name: Accessor
lines: This contains the accessor to the element which changed.
The type and the value of the accessor depends on the service.

items.name: Element
lines: This contains the element that was inserted or changed.

items.name: ReplacedElement
lines: This contains the element that was replaced or removed.
